title: Oscars 2017: Felicity Jones Looked Like A Real Life Disney Princess On The Red Carpet
text:
Oscars 2017: Felicity Jones Looked Like A Real Life Disney Princess On The Red Carpet It's Dior darling. 26/02/2017 23:26 Ellen Wallwork Senior Life Editor at   
The Oscars is the one occasion (other than your own wedding) when it is impossible to be overdressed and Felicity Jones really nailed the dress code with this stunning cross between a bridal/ballerina/princess gown. 
The British actress was an early arrival on the 89th Academy Awards red carpet and she opted for a full-skirted Dior gown. Jeff Kravitz via Getty Images Frazer Harrison via Getty Images Kevin Mazur via Getty Images 
The ‘Rogue One: A Star Wars Story’ actress is presenting an award at the ceremony and will see her film go up for best achievement in sound mixing and in visual effects. SEE ALSO
